DUBAI: German sportswear giant Adidas has collaborated with Dubai-based British artist Fink 22 on its latest Spring 2022 collection released this week. For the latest updates, follow us on Instagram @arabnews.lifestyle The new launch, titled Blue Version, includes jackets, leggings, T-shirts and sports bras in different shades of grey and blue. Adidas’s new drop features revamped products from the brand’s 1980s and 1990s designs.  A post shared by adidas DXB (@adidasdxb) For the launch, the painter created a large installation, currently on display in the Dubai Mall store in the UAE, that represents the power and beauty of the sea. Fink 22, who is also a photographer, used his splattering technique to paint shades of blue that appear to be dripping down the large canvas. Blue Version is Fink 22’s second collaboration with the sportswear label.